And we could see that there is not only one ideal wine for the buffalo bell mozzarella, there are different, original, surprising and linked to the territories, just like our product. We went looking for this wealth and above all we filled a gap: Finally, we have a method of study, a tool that we can convey to all. Thanks to this catalogue, the atavica question on which wine to match the mozzarella is overturned. From today we will ask: What region are you in? And according to the territory we will have an answer for everyone."
&nbsp;
He echoes the national president of Ais, Sandro Camilli: "The tasters of the Italian Sommelier Association have invested in this journey all their passion and expertise to suggest the best match path, exploring the richness of our denominations of origin. The large network of Ais Italia has allowed many professional sommeliers to be involved in this project, coming from the twenty-two regional delegations." &nbsp;

